{"items":[{"id":"36564","user":{"id":"333185","nickname":"Treubler","avatar_url":"https://creation.codemao.cn//490/YW5kXzEwMDFfMzMzMTg1XzBfMTY5MTg5OTU0NTM5OV9EU3lLZUZZWg==.jpg","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>出于楼上的压力，出个附件三：</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>好吧，举个例子：</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://s3.sinaimg.cn/middle/53e1f685taa9adc854192&amp;690\" alt=\"高一合力公式\"></p>\n<p>假设F1长100厘米，F2长200厘米，就可以说：朝F1方向施100的力，朝F2方向施200的力。</p>\n<p>那F的长度就是相当施于的力！</p>\n<p>那如何求呢？</p>\n<p>上文（附件二）提到，余弦定理的一特殊形式就是勾股定理。</p>\n<p>此题（详见附件一）中，刚好两力夹角就是90°！</p>\n<p>得出√100²+173.205²的算法。</p>\n<p>至于角度，就没算出来了<img src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/0b/wabi_thumb.gif\">……（算出来的60°是错的……）</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1503229171,"created_at":1503229171,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"36517","user":{"id":"179794","nickname":"ftxqgfudi","avatar_url":"https://cdn-community.codemao.cn/community_frontend/community_default_avatar/avatar_300x300_01.jpg","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>报……抱歉……你不附件还好，这个附件弄得头都大了……</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1503215094,"created_at":1503215094,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"36516","user":{"id":"333185","nickname":"Treubler","avatar_url":"https://creation.codemao.cn//490/YW5kXzEwMDFfMzMzMTg1XzBfMTY5MTg5OTU0NTM5OV9EU3lLZUZZWg==.jpg","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>楼主没耐心了，去换题了。</p>\n<p>此贴已坟</p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1503215005,"created_at":1503215005,"earliest_comments":[]},{"id":"36414","user":{"id":"333185","nickname":"Treubler","avatar_url":"https://creation.codemao.cn//490/YW5kXzEwMDFfMzMzMTg1XzBfMTY5MTg5OTU0NTM5OV9EU3lLZUZZWg==.jpg","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>附件二：平行四边形定理及余弦定理说明：</p>\n<p>平行四边形定则，可以理解成，F1与F2同时作用于某点的合力为平行四边形的对象线F方向。</p>\n<p>设F所对的角为A，F1与F2的夹角为B，</p>\n<p>余弦定理：</p>\n<p>c²=a²+b²-2abCOS∠C&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>平行四边形定则，合力F的计算公式为：F=根号下（F1²+F2²+2F1F2cosA）</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>推导过程如下：</p>\n<p>根据余弦定理知，</p>\n<p>(F<a rel=\"nofollow\"></a>)^2=(F1)^2+(F2)^2-2(F1)(F2)COSA；</p>\n<p>A=180-B；</p>\n<p>COSA=-CO喵；（锐角与钝角的余弦值差一个正负号，因为，锐角在一象限，钝角在二象限。余弦值=r/x）</p>\n<p>F=根号下（F1²+F2²+2F1F2cosA）</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://s3.sinaimg.cn/middle/53e1f685taa9adc854192&amp;690\" alt=\"高一合力公式\"></a></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>对于任意三角形，任何一边的</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\">平方</a></p>\n<p>等于其他两边平方的和减去这两边与它们夹角的余弦的两倍积，若三边为a，b，c 三角为A（<span>&nbsp;</span><img alt><span>&nbsp;</span><span>），B（</span><span>&nbsp;</span><img alt><span>&nbsp;</span><span>），C（</span><span>&nbsp;</span><img alt><span>&nbsp;</span><span>），则如下图所示，在△ABC中，</span></p>余弦定理表达式1\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\"></a><a rel=\"nofollow\"></a><a rel=\"nofollow\"></a><a rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt></a><img alt></p>\n<p>同理，也可描述为：</p>\n<p><img alt><img alt></p>\n<p>勾股定理是余弦定理的特例，当<span>&nbsp;</span><img alt><span>&nbsp;</span><span>为</span><span>&nbsp;</span><img alt><span>&nbsp;</span><span>时，</span><span>&nbsp;</span><img alt><span>&nbsp;</span><span>，余弦定理可简化为</span><span>&nbsp;</span><img alt><span>&nbsp;</span><span>，即</span><a rel=\"nofollow\">勾股定理</a><span>。</span></p>\n<p><sup>[2]</sup><a rel=\"nofollow\">&nbsp;</a><a rel=\"nofollow\"></a><a rel=\"nofollow\"></a><a rel=\"nofollow\"></a></p>余弦定理表达式2\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img alt></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img alt></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><img alt></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1503149054,"created_at":1503149054,"earliest_comments":[]}],"offset":0,"limit":30,"total":4,"counted":true}